@startuml Producer Blocked from Research-Only Data
title **Access Policy Filtering: Researcher-Only Data**\nA producer cannot see offers restricted to researchers

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #424242
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #9E9E9E
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam noteBorderColor #F9A825
skinparam sequenceGroupBackgroundColor #FFEBEE
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #C62828

actor "Will Thompson\n(Caney Fork rancher)" as Producer #E8F5E9
participant "Caney Fork\nCatalogue UI" as UI #E3F2FD
participant "Caney Fork\nEDC Connector" as CF_EDC #E3F2FD
participant "Governance\nKeycloak" as KC #F3E5F5
participant "Point Blue\nEDC Connector" as PB_EDC #E8F5E9

== Authentication ==

Producer -> UI : Opens catalogue, logs in
UI -> KC : OIDC redirect
KC --> Producer : Login page
Producer -> KC : Authenticates
note right of KC
  Token claims:
  **glcdi_membership**: "active"
  **glcdi_participant_type**: "producer"
  **glcdi_certification_status**: "regenerative-verified"
end note
KC --> UI : Access token

== Catalog Discovery ==

Producer -> UI : Browses Point Blue's data offers
UI -> CF_EDC : Request Point Blue catalog
CF_EDC -> PB_EDC : DSP Catalog Query\n(includes Caney Fork identity)

group Access Policy Evaluation [on Point Blue connector]
  PB_EDC -> PB_EDC : Evaluate **researchers-only** policy\nfor GHG Flux Measurements
  note right of PB_EDC #FFCDD2
    Checks token claims:
    1. glcdi_membership == "active" ? **YES**
    2. glcdi_participant_type in
       ["researcher","data-steward"] ?
       "producer" is NOT in list => **NO**
    => **HIDDEN** from catalog
  end note

  PB_EDC -> PB_EDC : Evaluate **members-only** policy\nfor Rangeland SOC Inventory
  note right of PB_EDC
    Checks token claims:
    1. glcdi_membership == "active" ? **YES**
    => **VISIBLE** in catalog
  end note

  PB_EDC -> PB_EDC : Evaluate **members-only** policy\nfor Weather Station Data
  note right of PB_EDC
    => **VISIBLE**
  end note

  PB_EDC -> PB_EDC : Evaluate **members-only** policy\nfor Biodiversity Surveys
  note right of PB_EDC
    => **VISIBLE**
  end note
end

PB_EDC --> CF_EDC : Catalog response\n(3 assets visible, GHG Flux **excluded**)
CF_EDC --> UI : Display available offers

note over Producer
  Will sees 3 of Point Blue's 5 assets.
  The GHG Flux Measurements and other
  researcher-only datasets are **not shown**
  - he doesn't even know they exist.

  This protects sensitive research data
  while still enabling peer benchmarking
  with the datasets marked members-only.
end note

Producer -> UI : Selects "Rangeland SOC Inventory"\nfor regional benchmarking
note over UI
  This asset uses **members-only** access
  + **non-commercial + attribution** contract.
  Will can proceed with contract negotiation
  for benchmarking purposes.
end note

@enduml
